{"tid":2305372,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林志玲喜慶46歲生日！　曬「托腮甜笑照」飄仙氣喊：一起好好的","createTime":"2020-11-29T14:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T15:38:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cad53d592cfd5e45edfb399dabc2446088f4f7ca","tid":2305372,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:42:19.000Z","msg":"台灣第一名模「志玲姐姐」林志玲，去年6月6日嫁給日本「放浪兄弟」（EXILE）成員AKIRA後，專注於家庭生活，減少了公開露面的次數。29日是她的46歲生日，她也特地在Instagram上曬出美照，吸引了許多網友前來按讚留言，為她送上生日祝福。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5303/d5303054.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5303%2Fd5303054.jpg&h=ed50a831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林志玲偶爾會透過IG分享日常。（圖／翻攝林志玲Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n林志玲29日在IG曬出一張美照，慶祝自己的46歲生日，並在內文寫下：「謝謝大家的祝福，也祝大家平安健康、內心愉悅、日子喜樂，一起好好度過今年的最後一個月。」照片中可看到她身穿白色荷花領上衣，用手拖著臉，巴掌大的小臉、水汪汪的大眼睛，以及超好的膚質，絲毫看不出真實年齡已經46歲，凍齡美貌讓許多粉絲都相當佩服與讚嘆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5303/d5303053.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5303%2Fd5303053.jpg&h=e795a128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林志玲29日迎來46歲生日。（圖／翻攝林志玲Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n林志玲的美照曬出3小時左右的時間就吸引了3萬多人按讚，網友紛紛送上祝福，留言道「祝姐姐永遠年輕美麗，生日快樂」、「是最美的人妻」、「越來越洋溢幸福氣息，比原來年輕不少，看來嫁對了人」、「人美心也美」。"},{"pid":"e2e39c28c32af3db6901dfec0c165a779e112ce7","tid":2305372,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"噢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知講咩好<br />\n有得屌屌唔屌"},{"pid":"d38f4d45083ac948ccfcd252fd9af945b3b4fa8a","tid":2305372,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2e39c28c32af3db6901dfec0c165a779e112ce7","tid":2305372,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"噢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知講咩好<br />\n有得屌屌唔屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:52:08.000Z","msg":"交俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1bc01257ed3c91bafe49db7f24cc6ec2c3d545","tid":2305372,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"都算幾靚的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb8e95d6f74f120d30f1822fe398131d8e7bbf","tid":2305372,"uid":325118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"老雞啦，唔好在扮靚妹啦"}]}